== NAME

Walma Screenshot - capture the screen, a window, or an user-defined area and
send it to Walma Whiteboard for collaborative drawing or save it to a file.

== SYNOPSIS

See

    walma-screenshot --help

== Configuration

You can manually configure Walma Whiteboard server in

    /etc/walma-screenshot.yml

For system wide configuration and for per user in

    ~/.config/walma-screenshot.yml

The syntax is following

    server: <server address>

Example

    server: http://walma.example.com


